'''Nigel Starmer-Smith''' is a [[British people|British]] [[rugby union]] journalist and commentator.

He played [[scrum half]] for [[Oxford University]], [[Harlequin F.C.|Harlequins]] and [[England national rugby union team|England]]. He has edited [[Rugby World]] magazine and for 15 years introduced [[Rugby Special]] for the [[BBC]].



